{"id":247984,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-长沙访民被遣返途中遭遇车祸（图）/","date":"2012-08-20T11:16:33Z","modified":"2012-08-20T11:16:33Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙访民被遣返途中遭遇车祸（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kyfhnPJ4q2s/UDIMx7-Uo6I/AAAAAAAALpY/0nSQOY_J740/s1600/1.jpg\"></a></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kyfhnPJ4q2s/UDIMx7-Uo6I/AAAAAAAALpY/0nSQOY_J740/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"290\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kyfhnPJ4q2s/UDIMx7-Uo6I/AAAAAAAALpY/0nSQOY_J740/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18 </span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>点左右，长沙</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位访民在被长沙驻京办从北京遣返回长沙的途中发生车祸，地点在湖北黄石段高速公路，押送访民的车辆车牌为京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">E47961</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位访民分别是潘建奇，何志华，杨小平，谭伟芝，李春义，艾运芝，肖利红，宋军良。其中谭伟芝伤势较重，遭遇撞击，头部、胸部疼痛。车祸原因是发生了追尾，尾部玻璃全部破碎。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>晚，访民艾运芝给访民刘华打来电话，说她现在被关在长沙高新区东方红镇的派出所内，李军所长正在给她做笔录。这些访民发生车祸后，不但没有被送到医院救治，反而关了起来。艾运芝说她现在还没有吃晚饭，艾运芝电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13467661899</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，长沙驻京办共派了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>辆车押送访民回长沙，一辆在湖北黄石段出了车祸，另一辆押送车情况也糟糕，一路上修了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次车，这车每次要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2-3</span><span>人推才能发动汽车，汽车还严重漏油。乘坐此车的访民反映说坐上此车心都提到了嗓门口了，一路胆战心惊，一路上下雨又是大雾的。当时被羁押在</span><span>久敬庄的访民说自己坐火车返回当地但黑保安不让。驻京办滥用职权，不仅非法限制访民的人身自由，剥夺公民信访的权利，还用黑公司，黑车，黑保安押送访民回当地，完全不把访民的生命安全当回事。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19 </span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点，长沙开福区访民李颂民、李香给朋友刘华发来信息：他们在久敬庄也被驻京办雇用汽车遣返回长沙。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2117103145700372814?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[21677,19196]}